So you're in the mood to watch a movie and you plug in your hdd. But if you're anything like me, you get overwhelmed by the sheer number of movies in that storage that you just can't make a choice. This  python script will scan all the movies on your hdd connect to IMDB and then provide a clean doc where your movies have been grouped genre wise and associates a plot synopsis and an IMDB movie rating to each movie. 

Happy Watching!



###########  Welcome to your MovieInfo Doc #############



Location: /media/hari/Expansion Drive/Movies/English/Movies/Horror 


The genres in your movie set are

Mystery
Drama
Sci-Fi
Adventure
Horror
Thriller
Crime




*****************Mystery****************



6 Souls   IMDB RATING:6.1   Plot:A female forensic psychiatrist discovers that all of one of her patient's multiple personalities are murder victims. She will have to find out what's happening before her time is finished.

julia's eyes   IMDB RATING:6.7   Plot:The story of a woman who is slowly losing her sight whilst trying to investigate the mysterious death of her twin sister.

Oculus   IMDB RATING:6.5   Plot:A woman tries to exonerate her brother, who was convicted of murder, by proving that the crime was committed by a supernatural phenomenon.

The Factory   IMDB RATING:5.8   Plot:An obsessed cop is on the trail of a serial killer prowling the streets of Buffalo, N.Y. but when his teenage daughter disappears, he drops any professional restraint to get the killer.

The Fourth Kind   IMDB RATING:5.9   Plot:A thriller involving an ongoing unsolved mystery in Alaska, where one town has seen an extraordinary number of unexplained disappearances during the past 40 years and there are accusations of a federal cover up.

The Gift   IMDB RATING:7.1   Plot:A young married couple's lives are thrown into a harrowing tailspin when an acquaintance from the husband's past brings mysterious gifts and a horrifying secret to light after more than 20 years.





*****************Drama****************



Silent House   IMDB RATING:5.3   Plot:A girl is trapped inside her family's lakeside retreat and becomes unable to contact the outside world as supernatural forces haunt the house with mysterious energy and consequences.





